sequenceDiagram
    participant Patient
    participant LoginPage as Login Page
    participant AuthCtrl as Auth Controller
    participant DB as Database

    Patient->>LoginPage: Open App
    Patient->>LoginPage: Enter Email & Password
    LoginPage->>AuthCtrl: Send Credentials
    AuthCtrl->>DB: Verify(email, password)
    DB-->>AuthCtrl: Valid / Invalid
    AuthCtrl-->>LoginPage: Auth Result

    alt Valid Credentials
        LoginPage->>LoginPage: Redirect to Dashboard
    else Invalid Credentials
        LoginPage->>Patient: Show "Invalid username or password"
    end
